OL,3,CCouncillors resign from Labour Party
OL,4,Ccondemning PM's leadership
OL,6,FA group of Labour councillors in
OL,7,FBroxtowe have announced their
OL,8,Fresignation from the party, sharply
OL,9,Fcriticising Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,10,Fleadership.
OL,12,FAround 20 members of the Broxtowe
OL,13,FBorough Council Labour group,
OL,14,Fincluding council leader Milan
OL,15,FRadulovic, accused Starmer of
OL,16,Fabandoning core Labour values.
