OL,3,CCouncillors resign from Labour Party
OL,4,Ccondemning PM's leadership
OL,6,FThey pointed to several issues, such
OL,7,Fas the means-testing of winter fuel
OL,8,Fpayments, the handling of the Waspi
OL,9,Fwomen's state pension age changes, and
OL,10,FLabour's response to Israel's actions
OL,11,Fin Gaza.
OL,13,F"It is with a heavy heart that we can
OL,14,Fno longer remain in a party that has
OL,15,Fdiscarded traditional Labour values
OL,16,Funder Keir Starmer's leadership," the
OL,17,Fgroup said in a statement.
