OL,3,CCouncillors resign from Labour Party
OL,4,Ccondemning PM's leadership
OL,6,F"From cutting the winter fuel
OL,7,Fallowance for 11 million pensioners to
OL,8,Fkeeping the two-child benefit cap for
OL,9,Fstruggling families, increasing bus
OL,10,Ffares across towns and cities,
OL,11,Fbetraying Waspi women pensioners, and
OL,12,Foffering a weak response to the
OL,13,Fgenocide in Gaza, this is not the
OL,14,FLabour Party we once campaigned for.
OL,15,FIt is not the party that Keir Starmer
OL,16,Fpromised.
