OL,3,CCouncillors resign from Labour Party
OL,4,Ccondemning PM's leadership
OL,6,FThis move comes after months of
OL,7,Ftension between Labour activists in
OL,8,FBroxtowe and the party's national
OL,9,Fleadership. Disagreements included the
OL,10,Fselection process for candidates in
OL,11,Fboth the upcoming general election and
OL,12,Fthe county council elections.
OL,14,FThe councillors claimed 10 of their
OL,15,Fmembers were "callously" blocked from
OL,16,Fstanding for Labour in May's local
OL,17,Felections for Nottinghamshire County
OL,18,FCouncil after voicing opposition to
OL,19,Fthe winter fuel policy.
