OL,6,FRemaining Labour councillors in
OL,7,FBroxtowe expressed disappointment over
OL,8,Fthe defections. In a statement, they
OL,9,Fsaid: "It is incredibly disappointing
OL,10,Fthat some councillors elected on a
OL,11,FLabour ticket just 18 months ago have
OL,12,Fnow chosen to sit as independents".
OL,14,F"However, these departures do not
OL,15,Faffect our commitment to serving the
OL,16,Fresidents of Broxtowe.
